00:56:29.865 --> 00:56:31.465
Keluar!

00:56:45.875 --> 00:56:46.915
Hei, Jun Kyung.

00:56:50.845 --> 00:56:52.315
Macam mana kau boleh pergi macam ni sahaja?

00:56:53.255 --> 00:56:55.585
